title: The Beyond Sun
description:
The Beyond Sun is a two-part visual project that consists of The Beyond sun film & The Beyond Sun magazine.
The Beyond Sun is a skate video / documentary filmed during the Beyond crew trips (2012-2013). The film is inspired by long-lasting & personal things inside rapidly changing skateboarding and surrounding culture. Filmed and edited by Pekka Harjula
The magazine also brings together all the trips that the Beyond crew made after it's previous project (Yours Truly Beyond). Photos and layout design by Samuli Härkönen
